command:example.maml:title: -------------------------- Example 1 --------------------------
command:example.dev:code: PS C:\> New-VeeamAgentConfig -Type Local -EncryptionPassword SuperSecret! -Restorepoints 99

dev:remarks.maml:para: This will configure a machine to backup its C drive to the largest secondary drive the machine has. It will encrypt the backups with the supplied password and keep 99 restore points.
